.DT 
add_skill_level 
Discworld living help 
add_skill_level 

Name
.SI 5
add_skill_level - Increase the skill level.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
int add_skill_level(string skill, int level, int exp);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This function increases the skill level of the living object by the amount
specified in the level var.  The exp var is used to specify how much
exp was spent on increaseing that skill.  The value returned by this
function is the new level of the skill.  This is the function used by
guilds and so on to increase levels of the players skills.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
query_skill, query_skill_bonus, query_skills
.EP
